snippet.title: A DUAL Against Starlo in GENOCIDE! Undertale Yellow - Dual
snippet.description:
Hello guys and welcome to an Undertale Fangame, and an Undertale Yellow Fangame as well, made by *Geno* called Dual and in this awesome fangame, Clover finally gets to have a proper dual against Starlo in Genocide / Vengeance and Ceroba dies trying to save her best friend...

Check out the game: https://gamejolt.com/games/genocidestarlo/884845

#Rockmanslayer #undertale #starlo

Twitter: https://twitter.com/rockmanslayer
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/rockmanslayer00
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/rockmanslayer00/
Tiktok: https://www.tiktok.com/@rockmanslayer00
Outro Theme: Onimusha Blade Warriors - Electronic Brain Realm (may not be the Outro depending on the video and game)
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JHUW6iWnWjI

Thanks for watching and have a fantastic day!
